packages/lib/package.json.description: Pako compression library verified for document version compression. Package: pako@2.1.0, Types: @types/pako@2.0.4. MIT+Zlib license, zero dependencies, ESM support, ~1.6MB unpacked. API: pako.deflate()/inflate() for sync compression, pako.Deflate/Inflate classes for streaming. React 19 compatible (no framework dependency). Performance: ~10 ops/sec deflate, ~130 ops/sec inflate on 1MB data. Perfect for JSON/HTML/text compression of document versions.
